Fencer				KEY:Fencer_Trait					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:You trained long hours as a youth with blades, either taking lessons in the genteel art of fencing from tutors paid for by your parents or by being taken under the wing of a disenfranchised fencer who may have turned to a life of crime.																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p. 11
