Magical Knack			KEY:Magical Knack_Trait				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:You were raised, either wholly or in part, by a magical creature, either after it found you abandoned in the woods or because your parents often left you in the care of a magical minion. This constant exposure to magic has made its mysteries easy for you to understand, even when you turn your mind to other devotions and tasks.					CHOOSE:USERINPUT|1|TITLE="Class Name"													BONUS:CASTERLEVEL|LIST|1																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p. 13
Magical Lineage			KEY:Magical Lineage_Trait			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:One of your parents was a gifted spellcaster who not only used metamagic often, but developed many magical items and perhaps even a new spell or two--and you have inherited a fragment of this greatness.																										CHOOSE:NUMCHOICES=1|SPELLS|SPELLTYPE=Arcane|SPELLTYPE=Divine																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p. 13
Magical Talent			KEY:Magical Talent_Trait			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Either from inborn talent, whimsy of the gods, or obsessive study of strange tomes, you have mastered the use of a cantrip.																																							CHOOSE:NUMCHOICES=1|SPELLS|SPELLTYPE=Arcane[LEVELMAX=0]|SPELLTYPE=Divine[LEVELMAX=0]																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p. 13
