Skeptic				KEY:Skeptic_Trait					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Growing up, you were always around magical effects to the extent that you realized that much of it was smoke and mirrors.																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p. 13

