Bully					KEY:Bully_Trait					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:You grew up in an environment where the meek were ignored and you often had to resort to threats or violence to be heard.																																																																																	BONUS:SKILL|Intimidate|1|TYPE=Trait																	CSKILL:Intimidate							SOURCEPAGE:p. 13
