Charming				KEY:Charming_Trait				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Blessed with good looks, you've come to depend on the fact that others find you attractive.																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p. 13
Child of the Streets		KEY:Child of the Streets_Trait		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:You grew up on the streets of a large city, and as a result you have developed a knack of knowing where to go and who to talk to when you're looking for some information.																																																																									BONUS:SKILL|Gather Information|1|TYPE=Trait															CSKILL:Gather Information					SOURCEPAGE:p. 13
