Poverty-Stricken			KEY:Poverty-Stricken_Trait			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:Your childhood was tough, and your parents had to make every copper piece count. Hunger was your constant companion, and you often had to live off the land or sleep in the wild.																																																																								BONUS:SKILL|Survival|1|TYPE=Trait																	CSKILL:Survival							SOURCEPAGE:p. 14
