Suspicious				KEY:Suspicious_Trait				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.SpecialQuality	DESC:You discovered at an early age that someone you trusted, perhaps an older sibling or a parent, had lied to you, and often, about something you had taken for granted, leaving you quick to question the claims of others.																																																																	BONUS:SKILL|Sense Motive|1|TYPE=Trait																CSKILL:Sense Motive						SOURCEPAGE:p. 14

